{"heading":"Israel will sing the song of Moses and acclaim: God speaks to heaven and earth; the children of Israel were known in the premortal life; God chose them in this life; they forgot the Rock of their salvation; He sent terror, a sword, and vengeance upon them; there is no God beside Him—Moses will be gathered to his people.","number":32,"verseCount":52,"verses":[[1,[["Give",["study-note-ref","a",[["Isa. 1:2","ot/isa/1.2"],"; ",["D&C 1:1 (1–2)","dc-testament/dc/1.1"],"."]]]," ear, O ye heavens, and I will speak; and ",["hear",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 41:1","dc-testament/dc/41.1"],"."]]],", O earth, the ",["words",["study-note-ref","c",[["Deut. 31:19","ot/deut/31.19"],"."]]]," of my mouth."]],[2,["My doctrine shall drop as the ",["rain",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Nature, Earth","tg/nature-earth"],"."]]],", my ",["speech",["study-note-ref","b",[["Isa. 55:11","ot/isa/55.11"],"."]]]," shall distil as the ",["dew",["study-note-ref","c",[["Hosea 14:5 (4–6)","ot/hosea/14.5"],"; ",["D&C 121:45","dc-testament/dc/121.45"],"; ",["128:19","dc-testament/dc/128.19"],"."]]],", as the small rain upon the tender herb, and as the showers upon the grass:"]],[3,["Because I will ",["publish",["study-note-ref","a",["HEB proclaim."]]]," the name of the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]],": ascribe ye greatness unto our God."]],[4,[["He is",["clarity-word"]]," the ",["Rock",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Rock","tg/rock"],"."]]],", his work ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," ",["perfect",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG God, Perfection of","tg/god-perfection-of"],"; ",["Perfection","tg/perfection"],"."]]],": for all his ways ",["are",["clarity-word"]]," ",["judgment",["study-note-ref","c",["HEB just, justice."]]],": a God of truth and without iniquity, ",["just",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG God, Justice of","tg/god-justice-of"],"; ",["Justice","tg/justice"],"."]]]," and right ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," he."]],[5,["They have corrupted themselves, ",["their",["study-note-ref","a",["HEB t