ould behave themselves strangely, ",["and",["clarity-word"]]," lest they should say, ",["",305],"Our hand ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," ",["high",["study-note-ref","a",["OR victorious."]]],", and the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," hath not done all this."]],[28,["For they ",["are",["clarity-word"]]," a nation void of counsel, neither ",["is there any",["clarity-word"]]," understanding in them."]],[29,["O that they were ",["wise",["study-note-ref","a",[["Ps. 81:13","ot/ps/81.13"],"; ",["D&C 111:11","dc-testament/dc/111.11"],"."]]],", ",["that",["clarity-word"]]," they understood this, ",["that",["clarity-word"]]," they would consider their latter ",["end",["study-note-ref","b",[["Lam. 1:9","ot/lam/1.9"],"."]]],"!"]],[30,["How should one chase a thousand, and two put ten thousand to ",["flight",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 133:58","dc-testament/dc/133.58"],"."]]],", except their Rock had sold them, and the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," had shut them up?"]],[31,["For their rock ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," not as our ",["Rock",["study-note-ref","a",[["2 Sam. 22:32","ot/2-sam/22.32"],"."]]],", even our enemies themselves ",["being",["clarity-word"]]," judges."]],[32,["For their vine ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," of the vine of ",["Sodom",["study-note-ref","a",[["Gen. 13:10 (10–13)","ot/gen/13.10"],"; ",["Isa. 3:9 (9–11)","ot/isa/3.9"],"."]]],", and of the fields of Gomorrah: their grapes ",["are",["clarity-word"]]," grapes of gall, their clusters ",["are",["clarity-word"]]," bitter:"]],[33,["Their ",["wine",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Word of Wisdom","tg/word-of-wisdom"],"."]]]," ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," the poison of ",["dragons",["study-note-ref","b",["HEB serpents."]]],", and the cruel venom of asps."]],[34,[["Is",["clarity-word"]]," not this laid up in store with me, ",["and",["clarity-word"]]," sealed up among my treasures?"]],[35,["To me ",["belongeth",["clarity-word"]]," ",["vengeance",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Retribution","tg/retribution"],"; ",["Vengeance","tg/vengeance"],"."]]],", and ",["recompence",["study-note-ref","b",[["Joel 3:4","ot/joel/3.4"],"."]]],"; their foot shall slide in ",["due",["clarity-word"]]," time: for the day of their ",["calamity",["study-note-ref","c",[["2 Pet. 2:3 (3–4)","nt/2-pet/2.3"],"."]]]," ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," at hand, and the things that shall come upon them make haste."]],[36,["For the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," shall ",["judge",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Jesus Christ, Judge","tg/jesus-christ-judge"],"."]]]," his people, and ",["repent",["study-note-ref","b",[["Num. 23:19","ot/num/23.19"],"."]]]," himself for his servants, when he seeth that ",["their",["clarity-word"]]," power is gone, and ",["there is",["clarity-word"]]," none ",["shut up, or left",["study-note-ref","c",["HEB left, bond or free."]]],"."]],[37,["And he shall say, Where ",["are",["clarity-word"]]," their ",["gods",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Idolatry","tg/idolatry"],"."]]],", ",["their",["clarity-word"]]," rock in whom they ",["trusted",["study-note-ref","b",[["Judg. 10:14","ot/judg/10.14"],"."]]],","]],[38,["Which did eat the fat of their sacrifices, ",["and",["clarity-word"]]," drank the wine of their drink offerings? let them rise up and help you, ",["and",["clarity-word"]]," be your protection."]],[39,["See now that I, ",["even",["clarity-word"]]," I, ",[["am",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 38:1","dc-testament/dc/38.1"],"."]]],["clarity-word"]]," he, and ",["there is",["clarity-word"]]," no god ",["with me",["study-note-ref","b",["OR beside me."]]],": ",["I",["study-note-ref","c",["HEB I bring about death, and I bring about life. ",["Ps. 68:20","ot/ps/68.20"],"."]]]," kill, and I make ",["alive",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Resurrection","tg/resurrection"],"."]]],"; I wound, and I heal: neither ",["is there any",["clarity-word"]]," that can deliver out of my hand."]],[40,["For I lift up my hand to heaven, and say, I ",["live",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 110:4 (2–4)","dc-testament/dc/110.4"],"."]]]," for ever."]],[41,["If I whet my glittering ",["sword",["study-note-ref","a",[["Isa. 66:16","ot/isa/66.16"],"; ",["D&C 87:6","dc-testament/dc/87.6"],"."]]],", and mine hand take hold on judgment; I will render vengeance to mine enemies, and will reward them that hate me."]],[42,["I will make mine arrows drunk with blood, and my sword shall devour flesh; ",["and that",["clarity-word"]]," with the blood of the slain and of the captives, from the beginning of revenges upon the enemy."]],[43,["Rejoice, O ye nations, ",["with",["clarity-word"]]," his people: for he will ",["avenge",["study-note-ref","a",[["Rev. 6:10","nt/rev/6.10"],"."]]]," the blood of his servants, and will render vengeance to his adversaries, and will be ",["merciful",["study-note-ref","b",[["Ps. 85:1","ot/ps/85.1"],"."]]]," unto his land, ",["and",["clarity-word"]]," to his people."]],[44,[["¶ ",["para-mark"]],"And Moses came and spake all the words of this ",["song",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG Singing","tg/singing"],"."]]]," in the ears of the people, he, and ",["Hoshea",["study-note-ref","b",["OR Joshua."]]]," the son of Nun."]],[45,["And Moses made an end of speaking all these words to ",["all Israel",["study-note-ref","a",["IE of all generations."]]],":"]],[46,["And he said unto them, Set your ",["hearts",["study-note-ref","a",[["Deut. 6:6","ot/deut/6.6"],"; ",["D&C 64:34","dc-testament/dc/64.34"],"."]]]," unto all the words which I testify among you this day, which ye shall command your ",["children",["study-note-ref","b",[["Eph. 6:4 (1–4)","nt/eph/6.4"],"."]]]," to observe to do, all the words of this law."]],[47,["For it ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," not a vain thing for you; because it ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," your life: and through this thing ye shall ",["prolong",["study-note-ref","a",[["Alma 9:16 (16–18)","bofm/alma/9.16"],"."]]]," ",["your",["clarity-word"]]," days in the land, whither ye go over Jordan to possess it."]],[48,["And the ",[["Lord",["small-caps"]],["deity-name"]]," spake unto Moses that selfsame day, saying,"]],[49,["Get thee up into this mountain Abarim, ",["unto",["clarity-word"]]," mount ",["Nebo",["study-note-ref","a",[["Num. 27:12 (12–14)","ot/num/27.12"],"; ",["33:47","ot/num/33.47"],"."]]],", which ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," in the land of Moab, that ",["is",["clarity-word"]]," ",["over against",["study-note-ref","b",["OR opposite."]]]," Jericho; and behold the land of Canaan, which I give unto the children of Israel for a possession:"]],[50,["And ",["die",["study-note-ref","a",[["Deut. 34:5 (1–8)","ot/deut/34.5"],"; ",["Josh. 1:1","ot/josh/1.1"],"."]]]," in the mount whither thou goest up, and be gathered unto thy people; as ",["Aaron",["study-note-ref","b",[["Num. 20:28 (24–28)","ot/num/20.28"],"."]]]," thy brother died in mount Hor, and was gathered unto his people:"]],[51,["Because ye ",["trespassed",["study-note-ref","a",[["Num. 20:12 (11–13)","ot/num/20.12"],"."]]]," against me among the children of Israel at the waters of ",["Meribah-Kadesh",["study-note-ref","b",[["Num. 27:14 (12–14)","ot/num/27.14"],"."]]],", in the wilderness of Zin; because ye sanctified me not in the midst of the children of Israel."]],[52,["Yet thou shalt see the land before ",["thee;",["clarity-word"]]," but thou shalt not go thither unto the land which I give the children of Israel."]]],"volume":"ot"}